# Setup anaconda environment ml1p13

1. Install flask
conda install flask

2. Copy alert_service.yaml to backend_service folder

# Start alert service
1. Start console and activate ml1p13 environment

2. Run command
start_alert_service.bat

3. check backend_service/logs/alert_service.log file

# Call alert service API
1. create logs folder for storing logs

2. Invoke corresponding api at AlertClient.py

3. check logs/alert_client.log file

